sub_title: Msc student in data science for food and health @ WUR
summary: hello, my name is Yongsoon Hwang and I am in 2nd year master's student in data science for food and health at Wageningen University & Research. I am an ambitious and energetic student of food and data science. I obtained a bachelor's degree in food technology and I am trying to maximize a synergy between food science and data science. I will be doing a thesis in the relevant domain from September to January 2024. I am actively looking for an internship in the domain as well
